== Scottish Parliament election 2011 ==
In the [[Scottish Parliament Election, 2011|2011 Scottish Parliament election]] the region elected MSPs as follows:
* 8 [[Scottish National Party]] MSPs (eight constituency members)
* 4 [[Scottish Labour Party|Labour]] MSPs (one constituency members and three additional member)
* 2 [[Scottish Conservative Party|Conservative]] MSPs (two additional members)
* 1 [[Scottish Green Party]] MSP (additional member)
* 1 [[Independent (politician)|Independent]] MSP (additional member)

